              <span id="reviewTextContainer2031314539" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6283448050559184044">Maybe it was hyped too much and my expectations were too high, but I didn&apos;t find this book life-changing. Interesting and helpful enough, but oddly, it didn&apos;t make me want to jump up and cook everything, which is what usually happens when I read such books. Also, for my own tastes, it was very meat-heavy.</span>
  <span id="freeText6283448050559184044" style="display:none">Maybe it was hyped too much and my expectations were too high, but I didn't find this book life-changing. Interesting and helpful enough, but oddly, it didn't make me want to jump up and cook everything, which is what usually happens when I read such books. Also, for my own tastes, it was very meat-heavy.</span>
  <a data-text-id="6283448050559184044" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

